 film&#39;s director, writer and producer Rian Johnson shared the snap on social media, writing: “A first look at Daniel Craig and Josh O&#39;Connor in the next Benoit Blanc mystery, Wake Up Dead Man. Working on it, much more to come!”</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr"> A first look at Daniel Craig and Josh O&#39;Connor in the next Benoit Blanc mystery, Wake Up Dead Man.努力，还有更多！ <a href="https://t.co/1cGPdPpAZ2">pic.twitter.com/1cGPdPpAZ2</a></p><p> — Rian Johnson (@rianjohnson) <a href="https://twitter.com/rianjohnson/status/1884994961948463425?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">January 30, 2025</a> </p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> In the <em>Knives Out 3</em> promotion picture shared by Johnson, Craig is seen standing by O&#39;Connor in a church aisle sporting a long hairstyle.帖子回复部分的粉丝对照片做出了积极反应，其中一位评论“非常兴奋！ One of my most anticipated of the year.”</p><p> Others asked for the film to have a theatrical release, writing in the replies: “Please make a theatrical release, I need to see this film in the cinema.”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/daniel-craig-netflix-knives-out-3-wake-up-dead-man-cinema-release-3809674">Back in November</a> , Craig said he hoped <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/netflix">Netflix</a> would give <i>Wake Up Dead Man</i> a longer cinema release. Speaking to <a href="https://variety.com/2024/film/features/daniel-craig-drew-starkey-queer-sex-gay-roles-1236199554/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Variety</i></a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/daniel-craig-netflix-knives-out-3-wake-up-dead-man-cinema-release-3809674">, when asked if he wishes that <i>Wake Up Dead Man</i> will play in cinemas for longer, Craig responded: “You know I do.”</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/glass-onion-review-knives-out-2-daniel-craig-3330126"><i>Glass Onion</i></a> , the most recent <i>Knives Out</i> instalment, did receive a theatrical release – but was only available on the big screen for a week before streaming exclusively on Netflix.</p><p> Craig told <em>Variety</em> : “Hopefully, Netflix will push it out a bit, and people will get to see it.我想和我说话的人 - 我想 - 他们想做的就是带家人去电影院看。 That&#39;s all they want to do.希望我们能给他们这种经验。”</p><p> The post <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/knives-out-3-first-look-shows-daniel-craigs-new-long-haired-benoit-blanc-3833283">&#39;Knives Out 3&#39; first look shows Daniel Craig&#39;s new long-haired Benoit Blanc</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
